Overview

Sample

Below is a sample analysis for a moral dilution study, with a total sample of N = 287, (female = 96, male = 190, non-binary/other = 1, prefer not to say 1, Mage = 35.7, SD = 10.1).

Student Sample

The majority of participants were from the student body: n = 0, (female = 0, male = 0, non-binary/other = 0, prefer not to say 0, Mage = NaN, SD = NA).

MTurk

In order to reach our pre-registered target sample size we recruited additional participants from MTurk: n = 287, (female = 96, male = 190, non-binary/other = 1, prefer not to say 1, Mage = 35.7, SD = 10.1).
